headline: Dolly Parton Serves Up Southern-Inspired Comfort Food with New Line of Single-Serve Frozen Meals
summary: Today, global icon Dolly Parton announced the expansion of her retail food line in collaboration with Conagra Brands (NYSE: CAG). This exciting launch introduces single-serve frozen meals that bring Dolly's cherished Southern-inspired favorites to homes across the nation in a convenient, no-hassle format.
